From ca005223cfffd8e7fb41e8aaefcf863c196976c7 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: =?UTF-8?q?J=C3=A9r=C3=B4me=20Duval?= <jerome.duval@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 30 Jun 2026 16:47:27 +0200
Subject: pretend to support kqueue on Haiku


